About this project...

## Installation

```bash
pip install yoctol-argparse
```

## Usage

main.py

```python
from yoctol_argparse import YoctolArgumentParser

parser = YoctolArgumentParser()
parser.add_argument('--fruit', choices=['apple', 'banana', 'lemon'])

```

## Test

```bash
make install-dev
make test
```


